            <abstract encodinganalog="520" label="Abstract">The Hadley mss., 1860-1869, consists of
                the Civil War letters of John Vestal Hadley, 1842-1915, who served from 1861-1865 in
                the seventh regiment, Indiana infantry, which was with the Army of the
                Potomac.</abstract>
